  "Description": {
    "English": "An electrified arrangement of mechanical wheels. Transforms stored energy into beams or propulsion, according to the specifications of weapons and laser attachments.<br><br>One of three core components, this forms the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">head</span> of a traditional Autophage <span class=\"name name-technology\">Voltaic Staff</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由机械轮盘构成的电器件。根据武器以及激光配件的不同规格，能够将储存的武器转化为光束或者是推动力。<br><br>作为三种核心构件之一，此物是传统自噬体<span class=\"name name-technology\">伏打长杖</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">头部</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "裝有機械輪的導電構造。可根據武器和雷射配件規格，將儲存能量轉化為光束或推進力。<br><br>三個核心元件之一，構成傳統自噬<span class=\"name name-technology\">伏打手杖</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">頭部</span>。"
  },
